      • retrieveUserGroups

        public ArrayList<UserGroup> retrieveUserGroups(String userIdString,
                                      long userId,
                                      boolean includePublicGroup)
        Retrieves groups that user is either a member of. Users are implicit members of the groups that they create so call also returns those groups
        Parameters:
        userIdString - user account identifier of user making request
        userId - id of account whose groups are being requested
        includePublicGroup - whether to include the public group that everyone is implicitly a member of
        Returns:
        list of groups that user is a member of

        public Set<Group> getAllGroups(Account account)

        Returns:
